lateral_limits: EGNPZ1 GOMUP 570000N 0100000W following the line of latitude to - 570000N 0095810.29W - 564500N 0095811.02W following the line of latitude to - 564500N 0100000W - 570000N 0100000W
vertical_limits: Upper Limit: FL 660 Lower Limit: FL 255
remarks: To prevent traffic from filling a flight plan across the NOTA/Scottish UIR boundary and conflicting with traffic entering or leaving Shanwick Oceanic airspace via GOMUP. Shall not prevent use of GOMUP as an Entry and Exit from FRA.
